T02D3353:35b-1: pradzny'a p'a ra mi t'a s'a dha nam /
T02D3353:35b-3: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3353:35b-4: bcom ldan 'das ma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3353:35b-5: sngon du bstan pa'i cho gas rang gi snying gar padma dkar po dang /
T02D3353:35b-6: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la pram dkar po bkod nas
T02D3353:35b-7: sngon du bstan pa bzhin du thams cad byas la
T02D3353:35b-8: / pram dang padma yongs su gyur pa las bcom ldan 'das ma zhal gcig ma /
T02D3353:36a-1: nyid rin po che'i dbu rgyan 'chang ba /
T02D3353:36a-2: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i po tis
T02D3353:36a-3: mtshan pa'i padma gnyis g-yon dang g-yas kyi logs kyi
T02D3353:36a-4: nang du longs kyin yang dag par bsnams shing bzung
T02D3353:36a-5: ba'i phyag gnyis kyis chos bshad pa'i phyag rgya kun
T02D3353:36a-6: nas bcings te / padma dkar po dang zla ba la rdo rje skyil krung can ma /
T02D3353:36a-7: lang tsho gsar la bab cing bdo ba /
T02D3353:36a-8: sna tshogs kyi na bza' dang rgyan gyis brgyan ba'i rab tu snang ba tsam mo //
T02D3353:36a-9: sna tshogs kyi 'od zer rab tu 'phros pa'i tshogs kyis nam mkha' bkang ste /
T02D3353:36a-10: mar me'i phreng ba lta bu thogs pa med pas /
T02D3353:36a-11: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma mang po
T02D3353:36a-12: 'phro zhing bsdu ba'i sbyor bas thams cad gcig gi
T02D3353:36a-13: rang bzhin du lhag par mos pas yang ji srid
T02D3353:36a-14: du shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma mngon
T02D3353:36a-15: du ma gyur pa de srid du bsgom par bya'o
T02D3353:36a-16: // de nas gal te dgod par byung bar gyur na /
T02D3353:36a-17: de la padma dkar po sna'i rtse mor sran tsa
T02D3353:36a-18: na ka'i tshad tsam bris pa lta bu rnam par
T02D3353:36a-19: bsgoms la / de la gnas pa'i shes rab kyi
T02D3353:36a-20: pha rol tu phyin ma shin tu phra ba brjod
T02D3353:36a-21: pa'i gzugs rtse gcig pa'i yid kyis yang dang yang
T02D3353:36a-22: du mngon du bya zhing bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3353:36a-23: de nas bskyed pa'i rim pa'i phyogs kyi sngags ni /
T02D3353:36a-25: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i phyogs kyi sngags med de /
T02D3353:36a-26: don dam pa'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i rnal 'byor pa gdams ngag thob pas so //
T02D3353:36a-27: dge 'dun sbyin gyi bu yis ni //
T02D3353:36a-28: rigs kyi ming gis 'bad pa yis //
T02D3353:36a-29: sems can kun gyi don gyi rgyur //
T02D3353:36a-30: sgrub thabs gsal po 'di bris so //
T02D3353:36a-31: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3353:36a-32: slob dpon dge 'dun sbyin gyi sras kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so //
T02D3353:36a-33: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
